column5: Seen this over on muskyhunter, looks like it would have been a large fish.
Looks like a massive head on that fish.  Too bad it had to end up in the condition shown.
That looks like it would have been a monster fish but all good things have to come to an end i guess
WOW. Must of been a tank. Too bad..

Any ice up there in P of B. I agree, Those are nice boots. Are they your sisters?. I know she likes rubbers.  LOL  P.S. are you in for going to the Vermillion Tourny. Call me at the office.   Stretch8z
